{"sectionId":755,"sectionIdLiteral":"755","humanId":"lesson-332","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"Fear binds the world. Forgiveness sets it free.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 332"},"annotation":"W-332","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-332\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"755#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>The ego makes illusions.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Truth undoes its evil dreams by shining them away.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Truth never makes attack.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>It merely is.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And by its presence is the mind recalled from fantasies, awaking to the real.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Forgiveness bids this presence enter in, and take its rightful place within the mind.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Without forgiveness is the mind in chains, believing in its own futility.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>Yet with forgiveness does the light shine through the dream of darkness, offering it hope, and giving it the means to realize the freedom that is its inheritance.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"755#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>We would not bind the world again today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Fear holds it prisoner.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And yet Your Love has given us the means to set it free.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Father, we would release it now.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>For as we offer freedom, it is given us.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"755#2:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>And we would not remain as prisoners, while You are holding freedom out to us.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"The ego makes illusions. Truth undoes its evil dreams by shining them away. Truth never makes attack. It merely is. And by its presence is the mind recalled from fantasies, awaking to the real.","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 332: Fear binds the world. Forgiveness‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†332 ‚ÄúFear binds the world. Forgiveness sets it free‚Äù: The ego makes illusions. Truth undoes its evil dreams by shining‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 332","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":755,"slugs":["lesson-332","fear-binds-the-world-forgiveness-sets-it-free"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 332","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":755,"slugs":["lesson-332","fear-binds-the-world-forgiveness-sets-it-free"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part